title: Aubrey's Traditional Creperie
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Western, Take-out, French, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Specializes in crepes and galettes from the Brittany region of France. Offers gourmet coffee, Bretton Cider, and other speciality drinks. The galettes can be made vegan with several vegan fillings including smoked tofu. The crepes can be made vegan as well.
